topic.title: 9 and my brother
topic.body:
9, It is what that is most relevant to my brother and he says the answer to all of our questions is 9. He gives example for it planets 9, Durga fast days 9, pregnancy 9. So he asks me what completes 9? Tell me what else do you find 9. (Neon).   91827...90
I haven't found the answer yet and tell me what else is 9, what is with this 9.
